DESCRIPTION:Hello friends! April 12 is my birthday and it is also the secon
 d sunday of the month. So I'll be at <a href="https://pioneerworks.org/prog
 rams/second-sundays-april-2026">PioneerWorks Second Sundays</a> this year. 
 I'd love to see you there!<br><br>There's going to be lots of events all da
 y\, and we can hang out in the garden. <i>If you plan on going remember to 
 RSVP on the PioneerWorks website.</i><br><br>Let me know if you're coming<b
 r><br>I'll probably get there around noon and stay until the end (around 6)
 . Afterward\, If we're up for it\, we can also go to Strong Rope Brewery ne
 arby.<br><br>Cheers\,<br>Cameron
